---
title: Contact
layout: layout.njk
contact: active
---

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-10 offset-sm-1 text-center">
      <h1>{{title}}</h1>
      <p>N'hésitez pas à nous contacter pour toutes demande de prestations. <br> Nous reviendrons vers vous au plus
        vite.<br></p>
      <div>
        <form name="contact" class="text-left" netlify>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label  for="first-name">Nom *</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="first-name" name="first-name" placeholder="John" required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label  for="last-name">Prénom *</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="last-name" name="last-name" placeholder="Doe" required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label  for="email">E-mail *</label>
            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" placeholder="john.doe@example.com"
              required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label  for="message">Message</label>
            <textarea type="text" class="form-control" id="message" name="message" rows="5"
              placeholder="votre message"></textarea>
          </div><i>* champs obligatoires</i>
          <br>
          <div>
            <input type="checkbox" id="checkbox" name="checkbox" required>
            <label for="checkbox">j'accepte de recevoir des e-mails de Charles Cantin *</label>
          </div>
          <br>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg ">ENVOYER</button>
        </form>
      </div><br>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
